%A6%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%99%E6%94%BE%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88-%E5%B0%8F%E7%AB%A5%E7%96%91%E5%90%B8%E5%85%A5%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E7%85%99%E4%B8%8D%E9%81%A9%E5%9A%8E%E5%93%AD</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190806/_2019080615022858151.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190806%2F_2019080615022858151.jpg&h=bf66fe24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有網民昨發起三罷及七區集會，其中一個集會在黃大仙廣場舉行，隨後演變成警民衝突，警方在龍翔道一帶多次施放催淚彈。網上流傳片段，指一名小朋友在黃大仙疑吸入催淚煙不適嚎哭，被抱起入升降機暫避。<br />\n<br />\n片段所見，一名小女孩掩著雙眼不斷嚎哭，被抱入升降機內暫避，其母及其餘兩名兒子隨後同樣入內暫避，另一名兒子亦以紙巾抹淚，懷疑同樣吸入催淚煙不適。母親其後用水為女兒清洗眼睛。"},{"pid":"05439178a5f3236f02cda2ec1632ca7e9bdfe2d3","tid":1425413,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5813966ca16188952f7cc90340bd86612a5a621","tid":1425413,"uid":131621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:25:27.000Z","msg":"嘩"},{"pid":"80683508c3dab514aab3562b97bd697e7761ad54","tid":1425413,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:47:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}